{"tid":1344684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"癱瘓地鐵=癱瘓交通=被罷工？","createTime":"2019-07-22T00:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T02:30:27.000Z","uid":212902,"like":17,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"67f7e74f9d2f1ccb31deb72f6aeb563ade2287f6","tid":1344684,"uid":212902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:09:25.000Z","msg":"癱瘓地鐵=癱瘓交通=被罷工？梗係唔係啦屌！（預咗畀人屌）<br />\n首先全港係咪得地鐵一種交通工具，冇地鐵搭就返唔到工？<br />\n再者假設真係得地鐵，係咪有人可以令地鐵全日癱瘓？<br />\n做唔到全日全面癱瘓交通，根本就做唔到強制全民大罷工。<br />\n你地而家搞地鐵只會令部份市民遲到，畀人話後生仔搞搞震。<br />\n諗住搞地鐵嘅巴絲，吸收過上一次嘅教訓，唔該醒下啦！"},{"pid":"8555298e79b486cf086bb97402390be43f8ebcf9","tid":1344684,"uid":212902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:11:08.000Z","msg":"預咗畀人屌"},{"pid":"d9a8298c84955f9305afa52d6af9b4b2ec3e1bf8","tid":1344684,"uid":212902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:11:18.000Z","msg":"預咗畀人屌"},{"pid":"7ebf4e73bdae513cab024b2c647e9054f379f6c4","tid":1344684,"uid":212902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:11:29.000Z","msg":"預咗畀人屌"},{"pid":"49a75b2cca3f9987a3a2de03d88d8dc1f511cfc9","tid":1344684,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:11:37.000Z","msg":"建制派及其政府 公然向香港市民發動恐怖襲擊！"},{"pid":"985b8a3b45402cc6ca6dd7becf49d727d75974f6","tid":1344684,"uid":212902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:11:39.000Z","msg":"預咗畀人屌"},{"pid":"b68ff1042ef72d8352f761841966745d9e583dea","tid":1344684,"uid":212902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:12:00.000Z","msg":"預咗畀人屌"},{"pid":"5a4cc48f0c0c86750fa76d9cd4b7dbe2101c9b25","tid":1344684,"uid":212902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:12:15.000Z","msg":"預咗畀人屌"},{"pid":"cb336f955b40f8f12cd0ceb9018d832c5e62df6f","tid":1344684,"uid":30771,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:12:34.000Z","msg":"呢個時候仲講民意？"},{"pid":"bdd04b4